Class planetSystem

java.lang.Object
src.PlanetSystem.planetSystem
public class planetSystem extends Object

      starName - the name of the central star
      temp - the temperature of the star
      pres - the pressure value of the star
      hum - the humidity level (must be 0.0 for stars)
      rad - the radiation level
